name: "Duck Stroll" by Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool)
description: [Digital drawing created with my phone from my good friend, Syd the Duck. I didn't have money to pay him to be a model, but luckily, he likes cookies... And I had those!] A duck strolling at night by the lake, looking like a serious hero! ---Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool)
